{"books":[{"id":"jfjb","name":"解放军报","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"","files":[],"article":{"dates":[{"year":1973,"month":1,"day":19}],"page_start":4,"page_end":4,"description":"","is_range_date":false,"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"title":"高原雷达兵之歌","authors":["赵长天"],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"上山"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山路陡，黄羊野兔惊呆；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山路险，秃鹰怕落悬崖。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"雷达兵呵多豪迈，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大步上山来。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哪里需要，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"队伍就往哪里开；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哪座山高，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就在哪里扎营寨。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"雷达、油机、弹药、器材，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"全用杠棒抬，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"战士的双肩呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"承得起整个新时代！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人渐高，山渐矮，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"登上顶峰望天外："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"呵，处处红旗展，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"祖国多可爱！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"登高歌一曲，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"迎风抒胸怀："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"万里空域保平安，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"岗上有我们在！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"战斗在冰山之巅"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"漫山的雪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"满壑的冰，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"冰雪的世界，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"消失了阵阵沙尘。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看不到一朵山花，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"找不到一丝绿茵。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在这冰山之巅，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"什么人能够生存？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"什么人能够生存——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"请看红色高原雷达兵！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这里有世界上最高的球场，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这里充满欢乐的歌声，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"火炉连的小花盆里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"已冒出冰山上第一点绿星……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那些目瞪口呆的资产阶级老爷，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"永远理解不了这儿的情景，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"因为我们的战士，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是用特殊材料铸成！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“挑水”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"队伍出发去“挑水”，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"钢钎铁锤手中提，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不用扁担和水桶，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“挑水”方法真稀奇。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"若问水井在哪里？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"几公里外冰河底。"}],"alias":""},"tags":[{"type":"文稿类型","name":"文章"}]}]}